value.0: Loki's Eye. A gem of great power fiercely protected by Loki's own progeny. It is rumored that when Loki returns he will use this great power to destroy the world as we know it. Loki is the only entity who can wield such a great power and those who attempt to steal it will suffer the wrath of the God of Chaos.
